IMAPStore fm-remote
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port  993
User jharr@ftml.net
PassCmd "pass mutt-wizard-fm"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore fm-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/fm/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/fm/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel fm
Expunge Both
Master :fm-remote:
Slave :fm-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Archive" "Drafts" "Sent\ Items" "Junk\ Mail" "Trash" "Waiting"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile


